com.amazon.clouddrive.utils

Class Optional<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amazon.clouddrive.utils.Optional<T>

  • public abstract class Optional<T>
extends java.lang.Object

    Defines a type that may or may not be present. An Optional that is not present can be created by calling absent().
